{"tid":1046276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國駐港總領事唐偉康稱不會就近日言論道歉","createTime":"2019-03-04T06:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T18:11:24.000Z","uid":41404,"like":203,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d5db7f113555224dd74ef47350eb132994689606","tid":1046276,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T06:20:06.000Z","msg":"美國駐港總領事唐偉康出席一個活動後，回應外交部駐港特派員公署就他近日的言論提出嚴正交涉他會否道歉。唐偉康表示，不會道歉，又說希望對方能看清他的言論內容，他只是表達意見，又說公開討論是好事。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，香港是一個好的商業城市，包括有好的營商環境及經濟自由度。<br />\n<br />\n唐偉康早前曾在演講中表示，中央政府對香港施加壓力，衝擊香港的政治生態和營商環境，又認為香港在近年有側重「一國」情況，例如首次有外國記者被驅逐出境、首次取締政黨、及首次有候選人因政治立場被取消參選資格，他擔心香港的高度自治能否持續，並威脅到香港的營商環境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445909-20190304.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445909-20190304.htm&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4CWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=06bcc93b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445909-20190304.htm&h=c27dec73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445909-20190304.htm</a>"},{"pid":"11f851ce69bbf56046bd5a9647ca02a073f41b42","tid":1046276,"uid":36775,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T06:30:35.000Z","msg":"唔啱聽就道歉，成地玻璃碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b76f85108eb4bc60b43ee92ecfbf98362fb94b","tid":1046276,"uid":24730,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T06:32:44.000Z","msg":"HO BALL"},{"pid":"679ad810ac9e68f997a689bd93e32829b60bd3de","tid":1046276,"uid":136216,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"美國註港領使根本就是代表美國官方立場，一個善言回應給中共和土共文革式批鬥;等睇香港關係法遲早死在這班仆街上&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"2a63402ac9a04705fcb65048ca9cdad2f613785f","tid":1046276,"uid":43117,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,